Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:54.66,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,There we go... Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:59.19,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you listen to your uncle. Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:00.36,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:02.24,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have your handkerchief? Your ticket? Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:04.36,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,A nice pair of shoes? Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:05.78,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't tell me that's everything? Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.78,0:01:08.04,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I made sure I packed the black ones. Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:11.67,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't forget your luggage on the bullet train, okay? Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:13.80,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't zone out and miss your stop. Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:15.30,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I got it! Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:19.15,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. I've been going there every year, so I'll be all right. Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:22.63,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, put on a hat. You'll get heat stroke. Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:25.06,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright! I'm fine. Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:28.90,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,See you! Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:59.22,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first time I met him Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:03.56,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was when I was six. Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:12.90,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\xshad6\yshad6\fad(1591,1644)\blur1\t(6696,8340,\blur10)\pos(968,5)}To the Forest of Firefly Lights Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:15.95,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On a hot summer day, Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:19.26,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got lost in the forest of the mountain god, Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.99,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}which was said to be where spirits lived. Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:27.55,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After running around searching for an exit Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:29.62,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I became so tired I couldn't move. Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:35.14,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I started crying from fear and loneliness, Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:38.44,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he appeared before me. Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:42.80,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Shorty! Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:04.53,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying? Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:11.66,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's a person! I'm saved! Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:26.18,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry. Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:31.39,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're a human child, right? Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.86,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If a human touches me, I'll disappear. Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:40.39,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,If a human...? Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.21,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a human? Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.17,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... something that lives in this forest. Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:51.59,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then... you're one of the spirits? Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:56.42,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,But... what do you mean by disappear? Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:24.44,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're really not human after all... Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:31.57,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,No human would hit a child like that! Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:37.13,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,To disappear means to be obliterated. Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:42.79,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spell that the mountain god placed upon me. Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.44,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If I get touched by a human, Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:49.26,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,that's the end. Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:55.05,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry. Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:56.66,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Here, shorty. Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.19,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Grab the other end. Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.34,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're lost, aren't you? Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.46,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead you out of the forest. Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.32,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:14.03,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I just tell you? Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:17.08,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I just... Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:34.45,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like going on a date! Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.99,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Not a very romantic one... Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.99,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You... aren't afraid. Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:49.62,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Of what? Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:51.67,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:58.40,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If you go straight, you'll hit the mountain path. Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:00.42,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Bye. Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:04.24,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you always going to be here? Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.09,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I come back here, can we meet again? Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:10.87,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This is the forest where the mountain god and spirits live. Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:14.97,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Set foot within, and you'll lose your way and be lost forever. Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:17.94,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't come here. Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.11,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the villagers say, right? Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.90,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Takegawa Hotaru. Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:29.11,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,You? Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:52.70,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'll be back tomorrow with a thank-you present! Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:53.51,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Bye! Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:54.64,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's Gin. Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:14.53,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru! Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.32,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Uncle! Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:21.01,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru, you idiot! Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:24.85,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,If you go into the forest on your own and get hurt, what are you gonna do? Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:38.64,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle. Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:39.62,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:43.10,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that there are spirits living in that forest? Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:46.95,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the mountain god's forest... Who knows. Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.78,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they say. Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:58.84,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I wanted to meet the spirits, so my friends and I often went into the forest. Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:05.35,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I never met any, but I had the feeling I'd occasionally spot something from the corner of my eye. Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:11.41,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,On summer nights, you could hear the sounds of the river coming from the forest.{*TLC hayashi?} Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:18.02,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,And now that I think about it, Iwa said she and her friends went and had fun at a summer festival in the forest. Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:22.83,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way the villagers would've held a festival in the forest. Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.95,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,So then, whose festival could it have been? Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:32.49,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,It started this crazy story that they must've snuck into a festival for the spirits. Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:38.22,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that takes me back! Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:41.50,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,We were so stupid back when we were kids. Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:15.06,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the forest where the mountain god and spirits live. Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:18.53,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Set foot within, and you'll lose your way and be lost forever. Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:43.56,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You came. Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:48.38,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd really come back. Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:50.25,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,You... Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:54.57,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,You waited for me! Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:01.47,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't learn, do you? Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:04.21,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy, I just... Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:05.39,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:08.79,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit hot here. Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.09,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go somewhere cooler? Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:12.08,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,What? Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.18,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.09,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you out of here again. Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:12.47,Default,Youkai1,0000,0000,0000,,Gin. Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:16.73,Default,Youkai1,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a human child? Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:20.24,Default,Youkai1,0000,0000,0000,,Can I eat it? Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:22.95,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No. Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:24.74,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,She's my friend. Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:26.60,Default,Youkai1,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.63,Default,Youkai1,0000,0000,0000,,Human child. Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:32.02,Default,Youkai1,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't touch Gin's skin. Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:38.26,Default,Youkai1,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, I'll eat you! Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.53,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Is that a fox? Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:50.52,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,He's another one of the spirits. Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:55.45,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,He transforms to scare people, but he's all bark and no bite.{He transforms to scare people, but he's actually cowardly and a good guy.} Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.00,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:04.03,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen a real spirit! Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.46,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,So they really do exist! Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:09.02,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Incredible! Fantastic! Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:09.02,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So what did you think I was? Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:15.54,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Gin, are you a No-Face or something? Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:18.28,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you wear a mask? Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:19.75,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No particular reason. Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:22.85,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind me. Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:24.80,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about yourself. Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:27.80,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you curious? Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:30.81,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I waited for you. Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:43.70,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The next day and the day after that, I went back to the forest. Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:50.07,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those summer days, I ran and played all around the mountain. Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.42,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, over here! Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:58.49,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's better over there. Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:02.34,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,There. Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:04.33,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:15.38,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though it was silly, Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:18.11,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it was so much fun. Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:45.13,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Did Gin fall asleep? Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:56.31,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's fine if I touch his mask, right? Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:15.60,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry! Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.00,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:22.12,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Attacking someone while they're asleep... You sure are a scary little lady. Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:24.50,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:27.30,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,you were pretending to sleep, weren't you? Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:31.09,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I looked normal, didn't I? Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:35.57,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you wearing that mask? Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:38.39,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't wear this mask, Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:40.79,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't look like a spirit, do I? Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:53.88,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're weird. Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.67,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Gin. Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:07.28,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:09.96,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,to come here tomorrow. Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:12.88,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I told you about it before, right? Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:16.52,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,That I'm just staying at my uncle's place for the summer? Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:20.76,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to go home tomorrow. Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:28.44,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be able to come again next year? Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.45,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:38.44,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is how summer Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.42,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}became something I looked forward to. Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:57.47,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gin waited for our promised summer. Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.82,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold! Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:04.24,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're weird. Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:06.52,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Of course the water is cold. Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:19.79,Default,Youkai2,0000,0000,0000,,Gin! Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:22.12,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Gin! Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.81,Default,Youkai2,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous, Gin. Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:27.09,Default,Youkai2,0000,0000,0000,,That's a human child. Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:30.96,Default,Youkai2,0000,0000,0000,,If she touches you, you'll disappear. Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:31.96,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:34.22,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:45.11,Default,Youkai2,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't touch him, human child. Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:47.37,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:57.73,Default,Group of youkai,0000,0000,0000,,Gin. Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:00.16,Default,Group of youkai,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful. Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:08.43,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,The spirits can touch him, right? Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.67,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two summers passed. Then three. {the original line for this is really bad, plz2tlc} Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.12,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru! Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:19.53,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:23.22,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru. Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:24.56,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hota— Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.65,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing? Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:36.70,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see your startled face, but... Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.22,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,At least when I'm around, Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:47.36,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,can you take off your mask every once in a while? Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:49.21,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:51.46,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but is there a reason? Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:54.56,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, but— Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:57.47,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Hota— Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:11.31,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That was close. Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:15.49,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:18.97,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Hotaru. Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:20.80,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.44,0:18:26.78,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:29.77,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gin. Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:39.51,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, don't ever touch me, okay? Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:45.60,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:57.17,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what! Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:09.00,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The next summer and the summer after that Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:12.28,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I visited the forest. Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:23.60,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving! Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.51,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Gin! I'm here again this year. Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:30.89,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.54,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've become a fifth grader. Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:37.25,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.82,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,you're starting to look like a woman. Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:42.32,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}am{\i0} a woman. Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:44.36,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go? Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:47.35,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:48.04,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:49.58,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is... Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.43,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:19:58.83,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:00.26,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:02.70,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm in middle school now, Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:07.82,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,a lot of my elementary school friends are in the same classes, so it doesn't really feel like anything changed. Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:10.43,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,But rather than that... Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:11.58,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Our ages are gradually getting closer. Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:18.66,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somehow, Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:23.61,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gin ages much more slowly than humans. Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:31.17,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Like this? Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:35.46,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. When I start running, let go, okay? Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.39,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go! Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:19.01,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As the years go by, my appearance changes, Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:24.26,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Gin is almost the same as the day we met. Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.33,0:22:06.42,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday I'll be older than Gin, won't I? Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.06,0:22:38.42,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hotaru. Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:40.33,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,I cut some watermelon. Let's eat. Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:42.89,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Yay! Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:49.60,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mom? Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.17,0:22:51.52,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Out shopping with your aunt. Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:54.46,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,They went to buy gifts for friends in Yokohama. Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.76,0:22:59.41,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,What time are you taking the bullet train tomorrow? Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.45,0:23:01.52,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:04.26,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,but they said I'll still be here until the afternoon. Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:06.34,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.18,0:23:11.99,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,This summer's weather was good, so the watermelons are sweet. Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:17.40,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,If it continues like this, then winter will be freezing. Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.47,0:23:19.75,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is it like that? Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:21.70,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,It's like that. Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:28.99,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Since this area's located between mountains and the ocean's far away, Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:31.91,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,the temperature difference between summer and winter is huge. Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:36.00,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,The cold of a winter that follows an especially hot summer Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:40.28,Default,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,could probably freeze the mountain god himself. Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.44,0:23:48.78,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Uncle... Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.77,0:23:53.78,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,A scarf? Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:55.02,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.53,0:23:57.04,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please use it in the winter, okay? Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.66,0:24:00.50,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Bye! Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.17,0:24:03.90,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.45,0:24:07.95,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,See you next year! Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.86,0:24:24.76,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Takegawa? Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.39,0:24:27.75,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be heading to your next class soon? Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.38,0:24:30.07,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're right! Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.07,0:24:31.66,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone left already. Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.66,0:24:33.21,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you later. Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.21,0:24:34.94,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Thanks. Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.85,0:24:57.86,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food. Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.86,0:24:58.43,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What? Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.83,0:25:00.18,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're done? Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.42,0:25:03.65,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you probably ate before dinner, didn't you? Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.65,0:25:05.40,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,If you snack, you'll gain weight. Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.40,0:25:07.02,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't eat anything! Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.02,0:25:08.89,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. I'm gonna take a bath! Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.35,0:25:40.21,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Takegawa. Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.03,0:25:43.35,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-ke-ga-wa. Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.75,0:25:46.49,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning. Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.79,0:25:47.53,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning. Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.88,0:25:50.52,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,There, near your feet. It's frozen. Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.96,0:25:57.43,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,You'll slip. It's dangerous. Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.12,0:26:03.03,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.38,0:26:12.12,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold today. Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.95,0:26:17.81,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you been a little out of it lately? Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.27,0:26:21.33,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you've always been that way, but... Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.05,0:26:24.03,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.19,0:26:27.39,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}see Gin. Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.93,0:26:53.83,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.17,0:26:58.33,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}touch Gin. Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.89,0:27:28.58,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your new uniform? Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.02,0:27:29.75,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.52,0:27:41.01,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Time really flies, doesn't it? Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.62,0:27:43.49,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're already in high school, huh. Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.49,0:27:44.47,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.18,0:27:56.61,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You don't come running at me anymore these days. Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.61,0:28:00.88,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I learned my lesson after all those beatings. Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.59,0:28:09.93,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it. Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.86,0:28:15.64,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,In three years, when I graduate, I plan on looking for a job here. Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.54,0:28:19.71,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can be with you more. Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.22,0:28:22.05,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,In autumn, Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.11,0:28:23.96,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,winter, Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.16,0:28:26.08,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,spring... Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.17,0:28:28.16,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Always. Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.04,0:28:29.66,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.64,0:28:36.44,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru. Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.04,0:28:40.89,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you about myself. Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.84,0:28:44.43,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a spirit. Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.45,0:28:46.25,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But, Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.51,0:28:48.99,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer human. Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.22,0:28:52.17,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like I was once a human, Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.17,0:28:53.79,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but when I was a baby, Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.79,0:28:55.73,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I was abandoned in this forest. Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.90,0:29:01.80,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'd only just been abandoned, so I cried helplessly{uh, what?} Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.05,0:29:06.44,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,as if to call back the parents who left me. Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.87,0:29:10.68,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,They say I didn't stop crying for a long time. Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.84,0:29:21.99,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I should've died then, Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.44,0:29:26.76,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but the mountain god appeared and cast a spell that allowed me to continue living. Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.00,0:29:32.31,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So that I never move on. Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.88,0:29:37.74,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm like a ghost. Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.51,0:29:41.30,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru. Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.42,0:29:44.14,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if you forget about me. Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.89,0:29:51.12,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,A body that's maintained by magic is very weak. Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.34,0:29:54.38,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If it touches a real human body, Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.80,0:29:56.74,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,the spell will break and the body will disappear. Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.74,0:29:58.71,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a fragile thing. Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.71,0:29:59.68,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How long can you— Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.68,0:30:01.68,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Something that disappears when touched... Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.38,0:30:03.99,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like snow, isn't it? Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.10,0:30:06.73,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Gin, Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.86,0:30:11.19,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of you during winter. Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.24,0:30:13.09,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Even during autumn Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.20,0:30:15.19,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,and spring. Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.61,0:30:17.35,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Gin, Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.21,0:30:20.50,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,don't forget about me. Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.97,0:30:23.16,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget. Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.92,0:30:30.07,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Time might separate us some day. Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.03,0:30:31.51,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,But, Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.57,0:30:33.51,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,even still, Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.15,0:30:35.52,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,until then, Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.39,0:30:37.82,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,let's stay together. Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.84,0:30:44.53,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit festival? Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.68,0:30:47.85,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No, a summer festival held by the spirits. Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.08,0:30:49.52,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much of a difference. Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.52,0:30:51.53,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The nuance is completely different! Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.06,0:30:53.22,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nuance? Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.14,0:30:58.04,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,When you were little, I thought you might get scared, so I didn't invite you. Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.79,0:31:02.03,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But tonight, can you sneak out of your house? Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.58,0:31:04.85,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted to go with you for a long time. Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.97,0:31:08.92,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want to go! Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.92,0:31:11.71,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Meet me at eight at our usual place. Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.21,0:31:16.85,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,But a festival filled with spirits sounds a little unnerving... Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.26,0:31:18.90,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, it's at night. Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.83,0:31:20.74,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.20,0:31:23.33,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,On the outside, it's not very different from a human festival. Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.93,0:31:26.57,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to mimic human festivals, after all. Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.28,0:31:29.76,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll protect you, Hotaru. Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.83,0:31:35.03,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,When you say things that, it makes me want to glomp you. Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.03,0:31:35.99,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Do it. Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.35,0:31:38.30,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously. Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.51,0:31:57.35,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait! Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.74,0:32:21.37,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. It's just like a human festival. Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.96,0:32:23.76,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are they all disguised as humans? Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.76,0:32:25.90,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Impressive, isn't it? Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.90,0:32:29.52,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that sometimes even humans unknowingly mix in. Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.04,0:32:32.89,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Like Iwa and her friends, huh? Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.89,0:32:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who? Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.84,0:32:38.68,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru. Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.12,0:32:42.05,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Tie this around your wrist. Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.52,0:32:43.47,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get lost. Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.51,0:32:50.42,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like going on a date! Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.27,0:32:53.02,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This {\i1}is{\i0} a date. Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.85,0:32:56.75,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go? Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.31,0:32:57.86,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.35,0:33:26.23,Default,Merchant,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.24,0:33:47.42,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Weird. Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.08,0:34:01.81,Default,Children,0000,0000,0000,,Ew, a couple! Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.81,0:34:03.21,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.06,0:34:17.43,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Look! That kid has a tail! Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.48,0:34:36.42,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry! Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.94,0:34:56.86,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that was so weird! Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.86,0:34:59.17,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone went all out with their disguises, didn't they? Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.17,0:35:01.25,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,It was like a mimicking competition! Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.25,0:35:02.67,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is it like this every year? Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.99,0:35:07.34,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, every time summer comes around... Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.60,0:35:10.44,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru, Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.16,0:35:14.59,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer wait for summer to come around. Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.19,0:35:21.59,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm away from you, even though I can't be around crowds, I want to go see you. Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.78,0:35:47.70,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That mask... Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.61,0:35:49.40,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Have it. Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.11,0:36:02.64,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He probably won't come to that place next summer. Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.07,0:36:08.39,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is definitely our last... Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.68,0:36:10.07,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.28,0:36:11.89,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.52,0:36:15.65,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.83,0:36:17.62,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thank you! Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.29,0:36:19.75,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, okay? Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.44,0:36:30.29,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Gin? Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.33,0:36:34.75,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Was that boy a human? Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.41,0:36:42.22,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Gin! Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.12,0:36:44.66,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, Hotaru! Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.26,0:36:47.11,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally touch you. Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.04,0:37:29.02,Default,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I love you. Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.77,0:37:30.47,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.64,0:37:32.95,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, too. Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.40,0:37:56.61,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Deep green. Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.90,0:37:59.68,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the mountain god's forest. Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.14,0:38:06.83,Default,Youkai1,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru. Thank you. Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.21,0:38:11.07,Default,Youkai2,0000,0000,0000,,We wanted to be with Gin forever, but... Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.07,0:38:16.31,Default,Youkai3,0000,0000,0000,,Gin wanted to touch a human. Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.73,0:38:20.72,Default,Youkai4,0000,0000,0000,,He finally got to be hugged by a human. Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.57,0:38:23.89,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I probably won't be able to Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.24,0:38:28.82,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}look forward to summer for a long time. Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.68,0:38:30.98,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My chest will hurt. Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.74,0:38:33.23,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My tears will be overflowing. Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.48,0:38:42.98,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this warmth in my hands and these summer memories will live on in my heart. Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.65,0:38:52.44,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, let's go. Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.33,0:38:58.50,Default,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let us go. Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.15,0:39:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED} Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.60,0:44:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(0,0)\bord0\blur1\p1\c&H000000&}m 1920 960 l 1920 1080 l 0 1080 l 0 960 l 1920 960 {p0} Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.45,0:40:03.38,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnGoodfish\fad(150,300)\blur4}The cicadas laugh out in song Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.28,0:40:10.02,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}to the red evening sunset Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.44,0:40:17.26,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}The way back home is long Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.12,0:40:24.41,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}but I promised to come here again tomorrow Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.16,0:40:40.44,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}The summer is in full bloom Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.74,0:40:54.58,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}making you look more beautiful than ever Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.48,0:41:15.75,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}I thought the tale would never end Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.77,0:41:22.55,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}but I realize now that something comes after Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.27,0:41:30.10,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}The crows too took flight Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.04,0:41:38.05,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}and went somewhere far, far away Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.73,0:41:54.27,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}The summer flies by Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.84,0:42:08.74,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}to hide away its treasures till next year Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.65,0:43:03.09,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}I'll never ever forget Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.37,0:43:10.57,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}those golden summer days Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.24,0:43:18.12,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}That summer which brought joy Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.41,0:43:25.70,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}to my boring everyday life Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.39,0:43:44.49,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}And look! Summer is here again Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.31,0:43:57.60,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}to help me keep my promise of that day Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.82,0:44:11.58,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}The summer is still in bloom Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.59,0:44:25.41,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,300)\blur4}making you look more beautiful than ever 